Field Description: District code - Unique 4 digit code assigned by DPI
School code - 4 digit code unique within district and assigned by DPI
School grade group. Grade ranges of schools in the same GRADE_GROUP may vary. See also LOW_GRADE and HIGH_GRADE
Count of the students expected to complete the term in the data group or subgroup
Count of students who dropped out during the school term in the data group or subgroup
Count of students who completed the school term in the data group or subgroup
Number of students who dropped out during the school term divided by the total expected to complete that school term in that data group or subgroup
